{
  "title": "ARIA dialog role must use document mode",
  "description": "This test ensures the dialog role does not invoke application mode in screen readers. The default mode (document) must be used. [ARIA 1.0 had language for the dialog role](https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.0/roles#dialog) that could suggest that application mode must be invoked. However, that language was [clarified in aria 1.1](https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.1/#dialog).",
